      <title>Cause of Bolt spells currently missing, Dev's please read and check</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=magicianbalance&amp;message.id=4407#M4407</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Okay, have spent about 3-400 casts testing WHY my bolts are not landing (no resist message, just not landing) I am fairly sure I have found the reason. Years ago was a bug where a player could stand in the way of the mob, and the bolt would "hit" him and not the mob, this bug is back.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;After testing from numerous positions of up elevated, down elevated from my target (i.e. hills) bolts would land if my pet/PC's were NOT in direct line between me and the mob, when I specifically stood behind my pet (even within 20 feet of the mob) or another player, my bolts would NOT land, not even a resist message.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;This leads me to believe that the old bug is back, please fix.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
