      <description>re-posting this here since it got ignored in the Veteran section.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;the lvl 70 mage aura Rathe's Strength has a serious stacking issue. If your in an area where you're not the only mage with the aura, the aura's keep overwriting each other. The main problem here is that unless your pet is right next to the other mage's pet, it wears off. Happens a lot on raids. I'll cast the aura on my pet, another mage will have it on his pet and his will overwrite mine if he comes near. Then he'll move a few feet away and the aura will wear off my pet. Its almost impossible to keep the aura on my pet, and having an aura thats supposed to last 30 minutes wear off 10 seconds after I cast it is very annoying. Please make it so the auras don't overwrite each other.</description>
